Name: Sakura Angels
About the game: 日本語バージョンダウンロード開始されました。 From the creators of Sakura Spirit... comes a brand-new angelic love comedy! Two girls, blessed with magical powers, are faced with the task of saving the lonely protagonist from the clutches of a mysterious witch and ancient evil, sealed away long ago by his ancestors. What does this sorceress want from our protagonist? Find out more in Sakura Angels!
